import React from 'react' import { useState } from 'react' import Calculator from './calculator' import './App.css' const App = () => { const [calc, setCalc] = useState('0') const [firstOperand, setFirstOperand] = useState(null) const [operator, setOperator] = useState(null) const [secondOperand, setSecondOperand] = useState(null) const operators = ['+', '-', 'x', '÷'] const updateDisplay = (value) => { setCalc(value) if (value === 'C/CE') { setCalc('0') setFirstOperand(null) setOperator(null) setSecondOperand(null) } if (value === 'OFF') { setCalc('') setFirstOperand(null) setOperator(null) setSecondOperand(null) } } return (
) } export default App
